The files are grouped into 16 series:
I. Correspondence;
II: Manuscripts;
III: Manuscripts by Others;
IV: Press, Publicity, Recognition;
V: Business / Administrative Files;
VI: Subject Files;
VII: Juvenilia;
VIII: Family and Biographical Files;
IX: Photographs;
X: Travel;
XI: Other Media;
XII: Periodicals;
XIII: Helen Henslee Doctorow;
XIV: Ephemera;
XV: New York University Creative Writing Program Files; and
XVI: Printed Material
